{
  "version": 1,
  "source_subtitle": "手机电车都在用，锂电池凭啥能充这么多次？_时间线01.srt",
  "output_audio": "手机电车都在用，锂电池凭啥能充这么多次？_时间线01_中文字幕直读_Yunyang.mp3",
  "mode": "verbatim_chinese_subtitle_audio",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunyangNeural",
  "rate": "+0%",
  "video_duration": "00:09:29.957",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "subtitle_001",
      "start": "00:00:01.133",
      "end": "00:00:04.033",
      "text": "你使用智能手机的每一秒都很疯狂"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_002",
      "start": "00:00:04.033",
      "end": "00:00:05.733",
      "text": "有化学反应"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_003",
      "start": "00:00:05.733",
      "end": "00:00:08.800",
      "text": "就像里面发生的小苏打火山"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_004",
      "start": "00:00:09.266",
      "end": "00:00:12.100",
      "text": "它看起来像一个没有许多活动部件的固体设备"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_005",
      "start": "00:00:12.100",
      "end": "00:00:13.133",
      "text": "但这是真的"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_006",
      "start": "00:00:13.800",
      "end": "00:00:14.866",
      "text": "电池内部"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_007",
      "start": "00:00:14.866",
      "end": "00:00:16.266",
      "text": "有化学反应"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_008",
      "start": "00:00:16.266",
      "end": "00:00:18.233",
      "text": "持续运行的"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_009",
      "start": "00:00:18.600",
      "end": "00:00:21.033",
      "text": "没有它，你的手机就会没电。"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_010",
      "start": "00:00:21.233",
      "end": "00:00:23.500",
      "text": "这是我们都很熟悉的"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_011",
      "start": "00:00:24.733",
      "end": "00:00:27.666",
      "text": "让我们调查一下这个锂离子电池"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_012",
      "start": "00:00:27.866",
      "end": "00:00:29.733",
      "text": "它如何为您的智能手机供电？"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_013",
      "start": "00:00:30.000",
      "end": "00:00:31.666",
      "text": "充电时会发生什么？"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_014",
      "start": "00:00:31.666",
      "end": "00:00:33.733",
      "text": "也许我们都想知道"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_015",
      "start": "00:00:33.933",
      "end": "00:00:35.466",
      "text": "为什么你的电池没电了？"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_016",
      "start": "00:00:35.466",
      "end": "00:00:37.333",
      "text": "一天中越来越早"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_017",
      "start": "00:00:37.600",
      "end": "00:00:39.000",
      "text": "来回答这些问题"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_018",
      "start": "00:00:39.000",
      "end": "00:00:41.733",
      "text": "让我们打开这个电池看看里面"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_019",
      "start": "00:00:43.700",
      "end": "00:00:47.066",
      "text": "那么首先，您的电池如何为智能手机供电？"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_020",
      "start": "00:00:47.866",
      "end": "00:00:49.866",
      "text": "让我们从我们知道的开始"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_021",
      "start": "00:00:50.733",
      "end": "00:00:52.800",
      "text": "所有电池都有正极端子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_022",
      "start": "00:00:52.800",
      "end": "00:00:53.866",
      "text": "和一个负终端"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_023",
      "start": "00:00:53.866",
      "end": "00:00:55.933",
      "text": "并提供电力或电力"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_024",
      "start": "00:00:55.933",
      "end": "00:00:57.800",
      "text": "到我们的便携式设备"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_025",
      "start": "00:00:58.000",
      "end": "00:01:00.733",
      "text": "所以电本质上是电子的流动"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_026",
      "start": "00:01:00.733",
      "end": "00:01:01.833",
      "text": "在我们的智能手机中"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_027",
      "start": "00:01:02.266",
      "end": "00:01:04.600",
      "text": "带负电荷的电子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_028",
      "start": "00:01:04.600",
      "end": "00:01:06.333",
      "text": "从负极流出"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_029",
      "start": "00:01:06.333",
      "end": "00:01:09.133",
      "text": "并运行扬声器或显示器之类的东西"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_030",
      "start": "00:01:09.133",
      "end": "00:01:11.666",
      "text": "最后到达正极"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_031",
      "start": "00:01:12.266",
      "end": "00:01:15.333",
      "text": "那么这些电子流是从哪里来的呢？"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_032",
      "start": "00:01:15.700",
      "end": "00:01:18.100",
      "text": "嗯，这是锂离子电池。"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_033",
      "start": "00:01:18.100",
      "end": "00:01:21.033",
      "text": "所以电子来自锂元素"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_034",
      "start": "00:01:21.600",
      "end": "00:01:22.733",
      "text": "在负端"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_035",
      "start": "00:01:22.733",
      "end": "00:01:25.000",
      "text": "技术上称为阳极"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_036",
      "start": "00:01:25.066",
      "end": "00:01:28.300",
      "text": "锂储存在碳石墨层之间"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_037",
      "start": "00:01:28.300",
      "end": "00:01:30.433",
      "text": "类似于你铅笔里的石墨"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_038",
      "start": "00:01:30.900",
      "end": "00:01:32.133",
      "text": "石墨有一种俏皮"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_039",
      "start": "00:01:32.133",
      "end": "00:01:34.266",
      "text": "层状平面的晶体结构"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_040",
      "start": "00:01:34.266",
      "end": "00:01:35.800",
      "text": "允许锂"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_041",
      "start": "00:01:35.800",
      "end": "00:01:38.666",
      "text": "楔入每一层之间"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_042",
      "start": "00:01:38.833",
      "end": "00:01:42.466",
      "text": "技术术语叫做嵌入"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_043",
      "start": "00:01:43.066",
      "end": "00:01:44.933",
      "text": "石墨的功能有点像"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_044",
      "start": "00:01:44.933",
      "end": "00:01:48.333",
      "text": "锂原子的稳定存储空间"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_045",
      "start": "00:01:49.300",
      "end": "00:01:50.733",
      "text": "好吧继续"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_046",
      "start": "00:01:51.233",
      "end": "00:01:53.633",
      "text": "锂元素的一个固有特性"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_047",
      "start": "00:01:53.633",
      "end": "00:01:54.933",
      "text": "它不喜欢它的"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_048",
      "start": "00:01:54.933",
      "end": "00:01:56.400",
      "text": "最外层电子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_049",
      "start": "00:01:56.500",
      "end": "00:01:58.433",
      "text": "它想放弃它"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_050",
      "start": "00:01:59.133",
      "end": "00:02:00.700",
      "text": "当有可用路径时"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_051",
      "start": "00:02:00.700",
      "end": "00:02:01.933",
      "text": "从负端"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_052",
      "start": "00:02:01.933",
      "end": "00:02:03.466",
      "text": "到正极"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_053",
      "start": "00:02:03.600",
      "end": "00:02:06.033",
      "text": "这个电子与锂原子分离"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_054",
      "start": "00:02:06.033",
      "end": "00:02:08.233",
      "text": "并开始前往另一边"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_055",
      "start": "00:02:09.000",
      "end": "00:02:09.900",
      "text": "同时"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_056",
      "start": "00:02:09.900",
      "end": "00:02:13.266",
      "text": "锂离开石墨变成正极"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_057",
      "start": "00:02:13.266",
      "end": "00:02:17.133",
      "text": "或1充电，现在称为锂离子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_058",
      "start": "00:02:17.666",
      "end": "00:02:21.000",
      "text": "仅供参考离子只是原子的花哨说法"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_059",
      "start": "00:02:21.000",
      "end": "00:02:22.933",
      "text": "谁失去或获得了一个电子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_060",
      "start": "00:02:22.933",
      "end": "00:02:24.500",
      "text": "因此被收费"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_061",
      "start": "00:02:24.800",
      "end": "00:02:27.100",
      "text": "当大量锂原子离开石墨"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_062",
      "start": "00:02:27.100",
      "end": "00:02:28.400",
      "text": "同时"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_063",
      "start": "00:02:28.466",
      "end": "00:02:30.666",
      "text": "形成了一股电子流"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_064",
      "start": "00:02:31.500",
      "end": "00:02:34.266",
      "text": "现在让我们跳到正极"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_065",
      "start": "00:02:34.266",
      "end": "00:02:36.733",
      "text": "技术上称为阴极"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_066",
      "start": "00:02:37.300",
      "end": "00:02:39.033",
      "text": "这里有钴"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_067",
      "start": "00:02:39.100",
      "end": "00:02:41.466",
      "text": "因为氧气而失去了一些电子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_068",
      "start": "00:02:41.466",
      "end": "00:02:43.866",
      "text": "从而使钴呈阳性或"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_069",
      "start": "00:02:44.033",
      "end": "00:02:48.833",
      "text": "4带电，结果它想重获一个电子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_070",
      "start": "00:02:49.100",
      "end": "00:02:51.700",
      "text": "所以当我们连接负极和正极端子时"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_071",
      "start": "00:02:51.700",
      "end": "00:02:53.000",
      "text": "到我们的智能手机"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_072",
      "start": "00:02:53.100",
      "end": "00:02:55.200",
      "text": "电子从锂中流出"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_073",
      "start": "00:02:55.200",
      "end": "00:02:57.500",
      "text": "它想放弃一个电子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_074",
      "start": "00:02:57.600",
      "end": "00:03:00.266",
      "text": "通过智能手机中的电路和组件"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_075",
      "start": "00:03:00.400",
      "end": "00:03:03.833",
      "text": "对于想要获得电子的钴"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_076",
      "start": "00:03:04.400",
      "end": "00:03:06.633",
      "text": "现在我们遇到了一个小问题"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_077",
      "start": "00:03:06.800",
      "end": "00:03:08.033",
      "text": "随着电子的流动"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_078",
      "start": "00:03:08.033",
      "end": "00:03:10.333",
      "text": "从负极到正极"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_079",
      "start": "00:03:10.400",
      "end": "00:03:11.266",
      "text": "钴的一面"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_080",
      "start": "00:03:11.266",
      "end": "00:03:13.866",
      "text": "越来越带负电荷"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_081",
      "start": "00:03:13.866",
      "end": "00:03:16.433",
      "text": "另一边带正电"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_082",
      "start": "00:03:16.533",
      "end": "00:03:19.266",
      "text": "是的，电子确实想朝这个方向流动"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_083",
      "start": "00:03:19.300",
      "end": "00:03:20.233",
      "text": "但同时"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_084",
      "start": "00:03:20.233",
      "end": "00:03:22.600",
      "text": "电子不喜欢流向一个区域"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_085",
      "start": "00:03:22.600",
      "end": "00:03:25.266",
      "text": "这是越来越多的负电荷"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_086",
      "start": "00:03:25.533",
      "end": "00:03:27.700",
      "text": "这是因为相反的电荷吸引"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_087",
      "start": "00:03:27.700",
      "end": "00:03:29.433",
      "text": "和类似的指控相斥"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_088",
      "start": "00:03:30.466",
      "end": "00:03:31.533",
      "text": "所以为了解决这个问题"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_089",
      "start": "00:03:31.533",
      "end": "00:03:34.833",
      "text": "我们给现在带正电荷的锂离子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_090",
      "start": "00:03:34.833",
      "end": "00:03:36.533",
      "text": "最近离开石墨的"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_091",
      "start": "00:03:36.733",
      "end": "00:03:39.000",
      "text": "一条通往另一边的道路"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_092",
      "start": "00:03:39.300",
      "end": "00:03:41.466",
      "text": "这条路称为电解质"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_093",
      "start": "00:03:41.500",
      "end": "00:03:42.333",
      "text": "及其功能"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_094",
      "start": "00:03:42.333",
      "end": "00:03:44.633",
      "text": "允许锂离子迁移"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_095",
      "start": "00:03:44.633",
      "end": "00:03:46.200",
      "text": "从一边过来"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_096",
      "start": "00:03:46.233",
      "end": "00:03:47.300",
      "text": "到另一个"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_097",
      "start": "00:03:47.466",
      "end": "00:03:49.833",
      "text": "同时不允许电子穿过它"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_098",
      "start": "00:03:50.466",
      "end": "00:03:52.833",
      "text": "当锂元素到达钴元素一侧时"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_099",
      "start": "00:03:52.866",
      "end": "00:03:55.833",
      "text": "它再次楔入或插入"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_100",
      "start": "00:03:55.833",
      "end": "00:03:58.833",
      "text": "用钴和氧变成锂钴"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_101",
      "start": "00:03:58.833",
      "end": "00:04:02.533",
      "text": "氧化锂无法重新获得电子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_102",
      "start": "00:04:02.600",
      "end": "00:04:04.666",
      "text": "那个电子去了钴"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_103",
      "start": "00:04:04.700",
      "end": "00:04:07.033",
      "text": "它只是平衡电荷堆积"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_104",
      "start": "00:04:09.133",
      "end": "00:04:10.633",
      "text": "让我们快速总结一下"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_105",
      "start": "00:04:11.033",
      "end": "00:04:12.866",
      "text": "这是一个完整的电池"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_106",
      "start": "00:04:13.033",
      "end": "00:04:13.833",
      "text": "全天"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_107",
      "start": "00:04:13.833",
      "end": "00:04:16.200",
      "text": "锂原子离开石墨层"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_108",
      "start": "00:04:16.200",
      "end": "00:04:18.000",
      "text": "并与它们的电子分离"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_109",
      "start": "00:04:18.000",
      "end": "00:04:20.000",
      "text": "变成锂离子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_110",
      "start": "00:04:20.033",
      "end": "00:04:22.633",
      "text": "电子从负极流出"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_111",
      "start": "00:04:22.633",
      "end": "00:04:25.500",
      "text": "通过智能手机中的电路和组件"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_112",
      "start": "00:04:25.566",
      "end": "00:04:27.666",
      "text": "并进入正终端"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_113",
      "start": "00:04:27.666",
      "end": "00:04:29.600",
      "text": "加入钴原子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_114",
      "start": "00:04:29.700",
      "end": "00:04:30.866",
      "text": "同时"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_115",
      "start": "00:04:30.866",
      "end": "00:04:33.666",
      "text": "锂离子穿过电解质"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_116",
      "start": "00:04:33.666",
      "end": "00:04:36.200",
      "text": "为了中和电荷堆积"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_117",
      "start": "00:04:36.200",
      "end": "00:04:38.066",
      "text": "并保持反应"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_118",
      "start": "00:04:38.200",
      "end": "00:04:41.000",
      "text": "这是反应的化学式"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_119",
      "start": "00:04:41.200",
      "end": "00:04:42.800",
      "text": "因此在一天结束时"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_120",
      "start": "00:04:42.800",
      "end": "00:04:46.266",
      "text": "几乎所有的锂都离开了石墨层"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_121",
      "start": "00:04:46.266",
      "end": "00:04:49.800",
      "text": "并加入钴成为锂钴氧化物"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_122",
      "start": "00:04:49.866",
      "end": "00:04:52.200",
      "text": "你的电池现在空了。"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_123",
      "start": "00:04:53.433",
      "end": "00:04:56.133",
      "text": "现在电池没电了，让我们给它充电。"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_124",
      "start": "00:04:56.133",
      "end": "00:04:58.700",
      "text": "我们插入智能手机，当我们这样做时"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_125",
      "start": "00:04:58.700",
      "end": "00:05:01.333",
      "text": "USB充电器施加更大的力"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_126",
      "start": "00:05:01.333",
      "end": "00:05:02.500",
      "text": "在电子流上"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_127",
      "start": "00:05:02.500",
      "end": "00:05:04.500",
      "text": "在相反的方向"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_128",
      "start": "00:05:04.866",
      "end": "00:05:07.200",
      "text": "电子从钴中被拉出"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_129",
      "start": "00:05:07.200",
      "end": "00:05:09.066",
      "text": "从而将钴返回其"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_130",
      "start": "00:05:09.233",
      "end": "00:05:12.333",
      "text": "4种状态并踢出锂离子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_131",
      "start": "00:05:12.666",
      "end": "00:05:13.600",
      "text": "在另一边"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_132",
      "start": "00:05:13.600",
      "end": "00:05:16.100",
      "text": "电子被压在石墨上"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_133",
      "start": "00:05:16.100",
      "end": "00:05:18.733",
      "text": "它将锂拉过电解质"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_134",
      "start": "00:05:18.900",
      "end": "00:05:20.900",
      "text": "回到石墨层"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_135",
      "start": "00:05:21.066",
      "end": "00:05:21.833",
      "text": "如你所见"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_136",
      "start": "00:05:21.833",
      "end": "00:05:24.800",
      "text": "这和之前的反应完全相反"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_137",
      "start": "00:05:24.800",
      "end": "00:05:27.200",
      "text": "这就是为什么这个电池是可充电的"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_138",
      "start": "00:05:27.800",
      "end": "00:05:30.300",
      "text": "锂和它的电子向一个方向移动"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_139",
      "start": "00:05:30.300",
      "end": "00:05:31.700",
      "text": "当你使用电话时"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_140",
      "start": "00:05:31.700",
      "end": "00:05:34.200",
      "text": "当你重新充电时，情况正好相反"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_141",
      "start": "00:05:36.333",
      "end": "00:05:37.033",
      "text": "好吧"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_142",
      "start": "00:05:37.033",
      "end": "00:05:40.833",
      "text": "所以现在让我们倒带并添加更多的注意细节"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_143",
      "start": "00:05:41.800",
      "end": "00:05:44.833",
      "text": "首先这两面不能碰"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_144",
      "start": "00:05:44.833",
      "end": "00:05:47.300",
      "text": "如果阳极和阴极接触"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_145",
      "start": "00:05:47.300",
      "end": "00:05:49.800",
      "text": "如果石墨里还有锂"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_146",
      "start": "00:05:50.000",
      "end": "00:05:53.300",
      "text": "化学反应会不受控制地加速"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_147",
      "start": "00:05:53.333",
      "end": "00:05:57.000",
      "text": "并引起火灾或通常是小爆炸"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_148",
      "start": "00:05:57.400",
      "end": "00:06:00.433",
      "text": "因此是一种不导电的半渗透隔板"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_149",
      "start": "00:06:00.433",
      "end": "00:06:02.933",
      "text": "允许锂离子通过"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_150",
      "start": "00:06:02.933",
      "end": "00:06:04.266",
      "text": "被放在中间"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_151",
      "start": "00:06:04.433",
      "end": "00:06:05.600",
      "text": "这种电解质"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_152",
      "start": "00:06:05.600",
      "end": "00:06:08.500",
      "text": "不是有效的屏障因为它是液体"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_153",
      "start": "00:06:09.266",
      "end": "00:06:11.433",
      "text": "第二件要注意的是石墨"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_154",
      "start": "00:06:11.433",
      "end": "00:06:12.800",
      "text": "和过氧化钴"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_155",
      "start": "00:06:12.800",
      "end": "00:06:14.066",
      "text": "不擅长收集"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_156",
      "start": "00:06:14.066",
      "end": "00:06:16.000",
      "text": "或者分配电子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_157",
      "start": "00:06:16.300",
      "end": "00:06:19.033",
      "text": "因此，导电铜层被添加到旁边"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_158",
      "start": "00:06:19.033",
      "end": "00:06:21.700",
      "text": "石墨和导电铝层"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_159",
      "start": "00:06:21.700",
      "end": "00:06:23.666",
      "text": "在过氧化钴旁边"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_160",
      "start": "00:06:23.733",
      "end": "00:06:27.233",
      "text": "这两层或片材称为收集器"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_161",
      "start": "00:06:27.233",
      "end": "00:06:28.700",
      "text": "好的到第三个"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_162",
      "start": "00:06:28.866",
      "end": "00:06:30.533",
      "text": "这些动画正在展示"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_163",
      "start": "00:06:31.000",
      "end": "00:06:33.900",
      "text": "100%的锂从阳极移动"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_164",
      "start": "00:06:33.900",
      "end": "00:06:35.733",
      "text": "到阴极再回来"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_165",
      "start": "00:06:36.000",
      "end": "00:06:37.300",
      "text": "但实际上"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_166",
      "start": "00:06:37.300",
      "end": "00:06:40.066",
      "text": "总会有一定比例的锂"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_167",
      "start": "00:06:40.066",
      "end": "00:06:41.600",
      "text": "仍然在阳极中"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_168",
      "start": "00:06:41.600",
      "end": "00:06:43.333",
      "text": "阴极和电解质"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_169",
      "start": "00:06:43.533",
      "end": "00:06:46.666",
      "text": "尽管电池充满电或放电"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_170",
      "start": "00:06:46.666",
      "end": "00:06:47.700",
      "text": "分别"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_171",
      "start": "00:06:48.433",
      "end": "00:06:49.900",
      "text": "继续到第四"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_172",
      "start": "00:06:49.900",
      "end": "00:06:52.900",
      "text": "为了最大限度地提高电池的容量"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_173",
      "start": "00:06:52.900",
      "end": "00:06:55.400",
      "text": "并让电池适合您的智能手机"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_174",
      "start": "00:06:55.500",
      "end": "00:06:57.233",
      "text": "所有这些层都折叠了"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_175",
      "start": "00:06:57.233",
      "end": "00:07:00.333",
      "text": "并包裹成长方形棱镜包装"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_176",
      "start": "00:07:01.700",
      "end": "00:07:01.800",
      "text": "唉"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_177",
      "start": "00:07:01.800",
      "end": "00:07:05.133",
      "text": "我知道这是很多，但第五名也是最后一名。"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_178",
      "start": "00:07:05.466",
      "end": "00:07:08.100",
      "text": "为了调节电流"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_179",
      "start": "00:07:08.200",
      "end": "00:07:09.733",
      "text": "添加了额外的电路"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_180",
      "start": "00:07:09.733",
      "end": "00:07:11.533",
      "text": "到电池顶部"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_181",
      "start": "00:07:11.866",
      "end": "00:07:14.133",
      "text": "该电路可防止过度充电"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_182",
      "start": "00:07:14.133",
      "end": "00:07:16.000",
      "text": "和电池损坏"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_183",
      "start": "00:07:17.600",
      "end": "00:07:18.733",
      "text": "那么决赛"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_184",
      "start": "00:07:19.733",
      "end": "00:07:23.600",
      "text": "为什么电池的最大容量会随着时间的推移而减少？"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_185",
      "start": "00:07:24.233",
      "end": "00:07:26.033",
      "text": "有几个原因"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_186",
      "start": "00:07:26.433",
      "end": "00:07:28.000",
      "text": "其中之一就是有时候"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_187",
      "start": "00:07:28.000",
      "end": "00:07:30.700",
      "text": "锂和入射电子"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_188",
      "start": "00:07:30.800",
      "end": "00:07:34.000",
      "text": "与电解质和有机溶剂反应形成"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_189",
      "start": "00:07:34.000",
      "end": "00:07:35.000",
      "text": "化合物"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_190",
      "start": "00:07:35.066",
      "end": "00:07:39.000",
      "text": "被称为固体电解质界面或Sei"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_191",
      "start": "00:07:39.266",
      "end": "00:07:43.266",
      "text": "SEIS不可逆地消耗锂和电解质"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_192",
      "start": "00:07:43.466",
      "end": "00:07:46.533",
      "text": "从而减少锂的总量"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_193",
      "start": "00:07:46.700",
      "end": "00:07:50.233",
      "text": "从而降低电池的最大容量"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_194",
      "start": "00:07:50.500",
      "end": "00:07:51.633",
      "text": "另一个原因是"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_195",
      "start": "00:07:51.633",
      "end": "00:07:53.333",
      "text": "当您将电池完全放电时"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_196",
      "start": "00:07:53.333",
      "end": "00:07:54.400",
      "text": "直到它死了"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_197",
      "start": "00:07:54.433",
      "end": "00:07:57.866",
      "text": "它会导致钴侧有太多的锂"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_198",
      "start": "00:07:57.866",
      "end": "00:08:01.033",
      "text": "导致锂的不可逆生成"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_199",
      "start": "00:08:01.033",
      "end": "00:08:02.633",
      "text": "氧化物和钴"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_200",
      "start": "00:08:02.700",
      "end": "00:08:06.200",
      "text": "2氧化物这些化合物停留在那个状态"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_201",
      "start": "00:08:06.200",
      "end": "00:08:06.866",
      "text": "从而"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_202",
      "start": "00:08:06.866",
      "end": "00:08:09.533",
      "text": "减少锂和钴的量"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_203",
      "start": "00:08:09.533",
      "end": "00:08:10.900",
      "text": "供将来使用"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_204",
      "start": "00:08:10.933",
      "end": "00:08:13.233",
      "text": "所以一个提示是不要让你的电池运行"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_205",
      "start": "00:08:13.233",
      "end": "00:08:14.400",
      "text": "直到它空了"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_206",
      "start": "00:08:14.600",
      "end": "00:08:16.600",
      "text": "最好给电池充电"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_207",
      "start": "00:08:16.600",
      "end": "00:08:19.533",
      "text": "30%或40%比让它一直运行到死"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_208",
      "start": "00:08:20.900",
      "end": "00:08:22.400",
      "text": "那就差不多结束了"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_209",
      "start": "00:08:22.833",
      "end": "00:08:24.033",
      "text": "说到电池"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_210",
      "start": "00:08:24.033",
      "end": "00:08:26.033",
      "text": "有数百种不同的化学物质"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_211",
      "start": "00:08:26.033",
      "end": "00:08:28.233",
      "text": "以及让它们发挥作用的化合物"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_212",
      "start": "00:08:28.233",
      "end": "00:08:30.666",
      "text": "但它们都遵循相似的原理"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_213",
      "start": "00:08:30.933",
      "end": "00:08:33.200",
      "text": "你只需要三种材料"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_214",
      "start": "00:08:33.266",
      "end": "00:08:35.033",
      "text": "想要电子的人"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_215",
      "start": "00:08:35.033",
      "end": "00:08:37.433",
      "text": "一个想放弃电子的人"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_216",
      "start": "00:08:37.433",
      "end": "00:08:39.500",
      "text": "然后是电荷积累的路径"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_217",
      "start": "00:08:39.500",
      "end": "00:08:40.900",
      "text": "中和"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_218",
      "start": "00:08:41.633",
      "end": "00:08:42.700",
      "text": "感谢收看"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_219",
      "start": "00:08:42.700",
      "end": "00:08:45.133",
      "text": "这里有三个问题我将留给你们"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_220",
      "start": "00:08:45.400",
      "end": "00:08:47.066",
      "text": "在评论中讨论它们"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_221",
      "start": "00:08:47.300",
      "end": "00:08:50.066",
      "text": "也在评论中提问"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_222",
      "start": "00:08:50.100",
      "end": "00:08:51.000",
      "text": "如果你做了"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_223",
      "start": "00:08:51.000",
      "end": "00:08:54.000",
      "text": "我将确定首要问题以供进一步讨论"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_224",
      "start": "00:08:54.300",
      "end": "00:08:55.666",
      "text": "别忘了订阅"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_225",
      "start": "00:08:55.666",
      "end": "00:08:57.700",
      "text": "告诉你的朋友和家人一些事情"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_226",
      "start": "00:08:57.700",
      "end": "00:08:58.600",
      "text": "你今天学到了"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_227",
      "start": "00:08:58.866",
      "end": "00:09:02.266",
      "text": "这一集是关于锂离子智能手机电池的"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_228",
      "start": "00:09:02.266",
      "end": "00:09:03.466",
      "text": "它的分支"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_229",
      "start": "00:09:03.466",
      "end": "00:09:05.233",
      "text": "到电动汽车电池"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_230",
      "start": "00:09:05.233",
      "end": "00:09:07.200",
      "text": "学习工程讨论"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_231",
      "start": "00:09:07.266",
      "end": "00:09:08.800",
      "text": "我们建议您看看"
    },
    {
      "id": "subtitle_232",
      "start": "00:09:10.033",
      "end": "00:09:13.200",
      "text": "它还连接到原电池和伏打电池"
